cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.SI, cs.CY, cs.SD 

This paper discusses approaches for epidemic intelligence that use textual datasets, which falls under the domain of natural language processing (NLP). Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves information retrieval (IR) techniques for selecting relevant text, which makes cs.IR (Information Retrieval) another likely category. The paper also discusses the use of resources and evaluation strategies, which could fall under cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) and cs.CY (Computers and Society). Finally, the paper involves the use of machine learning techniques for health event detection, which could fall under cs.SD (Software Engineering).
